title: Beautifully well maintained 4 bed 2 bath home with playhouse!
posting_body: Beautiful home in a quiet neighborhood.
House is stunning with high ceilings, engineered hardwood flooring, stainless steel kitchen appliances, gas fireplace.
This one-story, light and airy, warm and inviting home with open floor plan has been impeccably cared for.
New interior paint, now a soft shade of gray in the open living area.
Has a large room with French doors that could be used as a den/office, second family room or fourth bedroom.
Master bathroom has dual sinks, separate shower, walk in closet and very large tub.
Child's playhouse, storage shed, patio and veggie patch in backyard.
Three car garage, I'm sorry but family pets are not allowed at this property.
Renter's liability insurance required prior to move-in.
No smoking allowed on the property.
HOA fees and irrigation water paid by property owner.
